>A few rooms later and you’re back at the main foyer
>There’s the exit
>You throw open the front doors and head out into the late night
>Haywood’s car is gone, but he left you a copious amount of texts and missed calls
>”Dude, where are you?” he says when you pick up the next frantic ring
